leaders in your professions

00:38:44.910 --> 00:38:48.220
and in your communities
and that the continuing

00:38:48.220 --> 00:38:52.440
support of your fellow alumni,
both your peers and those

00:38:52.440 --> 00:38:55.840
who have preceded you,
will help sustain you

00:38:55.840 --> 00:38:57.570
as you change the world.

00:38:57.570 --> 00:39:00.040
Congratulations, class of 2014.

